sentences: Oguntade Adewale Damola (born 27 June 1989), professionally known as Ajimovoix, is a Nigerian musician and producer.

He gained widespread attention after releasing "Focus Dance Beat" In 2020, and it went viral in 2021 which Reached Top 100 on Apple Music, Number 1 on Tunde Ednut top 10, and number 2 on Instagram Creator popular tracklist in July now tends to drop his first 5 track EP as a Music Producer, 'That Unserious Boy' under Horus Music Nigeria.
